snippet.title: Mosaic trailer - PC Gaming Show 2019
snippet.description:
This bleak adventure game not only looks terrifying but also scarily relevant to today's "always online" mentality.

You can find more information here: https://www.pcgamer.com/mysterious-adventure-game-mosaic-gets-a-new-trailer-at-the-pc-gaming-show/
